@startuml Knowledge Graph Builder Workflow

skin rose
skinparam Style strictuml
title Knowledge Graph Builder Workflow

actor User
participant "API" as API
participant "Document extraction" as DocumentExtraction
participant "chunking" as Chunking
participant "Embedding" as Embedding
participant "KG extraction" as KGExtraction
participant "Graph Builder" as GraphBuilder
participant "Neo4j" as Neo4j

User -> API: Upload document
API -> DocumentExtraction: Extract text from document
DocumentExtraction -> Chunking: Split text into chunks
Chunking -> KGExtraction: Extract entities and relationships
loop for each chunk
    Embedding -> GraphBuilder: Generate embeddings for chunk
    KGExtraction -> GraphBuilder: Build graph with extracted entities and relationships
    GraphBuilder -> Neo4j: Store graph in Neo4j database
end
GraphBuilder --> API: Return graph document
API --> User: graph document response

@enduml